reviewText: I thought that the DVD set was amazing, in fact ordering the entire series has given me a much broader view of what the secret teaches. I think you have to be a fan of the Western Mystery Tradition to really get what you want out of these DVDs. I loved Magickal Egypt and added these to my list of must haves. There are lots of youtube trailers for these guys...try before you buy! I LOVED ALL OF THEM!
